they are quite a lot.

01:08:07.749 --> 01:08:12.974
Too many! Big problem.

01:08:13.175 --> 01:08:18.328
Alright. You can have them. With three
Atharva Sheersha we should finish all…

01:08:18.529 --> 01:08:23.607
you look after, say, “Now it’s over time”.

01:08:23.830 --> 01:08:33.751
