that? Gavin: Yes.

01:08:41.179 --> 01:08:45.778
Shri Mataji: And then you can do the Devi’s
names, I think. Gavin: It’s fine.

01:08:46.273 --> 01:08:52.579
Shri Mataji: But - while doing
the Krishna’s names

01:08:57.095 --> 01:09:03.376
you can wash the hands and the Feet.
