01:09:05.792 --> 01:09:12.330
you can dress Me up, it’s possible;

01:09:15.074 --> 01:09:19.005
or if you know some songs of Krishna,
instead of taking His names,

01:09:19.206 --> 01:09:21.864
you can sing it.

