Gavin: People are there. Shri Mataji: Eh?
Gavin: The music people are there.

01:09:30.892 --> 01:09:34.059
Shri Mataji: All right, is all right.

01:09:38.109 --> 01:09:43.230
You see, could be better to have it,
music, a little.

01:09:43.440 --> 01:09:47.500
Again it becomes very serious, you see.

01:09:58.848 --> 01:10:03.122
All right. So you can sit next to the
thing. Gavin: Yes.

01:10:03.323 --> 01:10:09.126
Shri Mataji: And who else knows the
mantras? I think, Guido can come.

01:10:09.723 --> 01:10:12.823
Here, here, this side.

01:10:27.443 --> 01:10:31.492
