Krishna’s flower is called as Krishna
kamal.

01:11:09.127 --> 01:11:12.963
That type don’t grows here. It’s
a beautiful flower,

01:11:13.164 --> 01:11:19.200
called as Krishna kamal. Is a colour
of that, that sky colour.

01:11:19.401 --> 01:11:22.266
That’s Shri Krishna colour. (Hindi)

01:11:22.467 --> 01:11:29.042
Possibly, possibly, I think I saw it
in Switzerland in your house,

01:11:29.243 --> 01:11:32.145
first house, a Krishna kamal flower.
You had it there?

01:11:32.346 --> 01:11:36.726
Yogi: Yes…
Shri Mataji: Is a kind of a creeper.

01:11:36.927 --> 01:11:44.023
