All right. All right.

01:21:07.313 --> 01:21:09.751
May God bless you.

01:21:22.359 --> 01:21:25.371
May God bless you.

01:22:08.219 --> 01:22:12.560
May God bless you. Good. Excellent.

01:22:34.522 --> 01:22:38.048
All right. Excellent.

