You can sing the song of Ganesha now,
it’s all right. You can sing the song.

01:22:56.795 --> 01:23:00.195
Yogi: Shri Ganesha?
Shri Mataji: It’s good.

01:23:00.404 --> 01:23:02.957
They can sing the song
of Shri Ganesha’s song.

01:23:03.166 --> 01:23:10.076
It is – will be better. Should be more
music in Shri Krishna’s…

01:23:29.502 --> 01:23:36.260
Yogi 1: Which song? Yogi 2: Shri Ganesha.
