01:28:52.664 --> 01:28:57.904
Now. Christine? Christine?

01:28:59.098 --> 01:29:04.307
You get about six ladies from France.

01:29:09.133 --> 01:29:11.991
Married ladies.

01:29:32.846 --> 01:29:37.127
Yogi: Catherine from Mulhouse, Catherine
from Mulhouse.

