Oh beautiful!

03:07:29.096 --> 03:07:34.829
Oh! Done so well, I must say!

03:07:35.540 --> 03:07:40.147
Beautiful, beautiful, what an ashram!

03:07:40.363 --> 03:07:44.561
I may settle down in Switzerland!

03:07:47.926 --> 03:07:52.150
Yogi: Shri Mataji, may this house stay
in your house,

03:07:52.359 --> 03:07:54.870
so that we get the protection of You
all the time.

03:07:55.071 --> 03:07:58.634
Shri Mataji: All right, thank you
very much.

03:08:09.323 --> 03:08:16.238
Beautiful, eh? How far is it now?
Started?

03:08:16.439 --> 03:08:19.634
Yogi: The floor’s basement is done already.
Shri Mataji: Oh oh!

03:08:19.835 --> 03:08:21.366
Other yogi: The concrete is put,
Shri Mataji. Shri Mataji: Good, good.

