...are going to come on the seventh
of September.

03:08:26.501 --> 03:08:28.516
Shri Mataji: Oh, I... Yogi: So when You
come to Switzerland, Shri Mataji,

03:08:28.717 --> 03:08:31.058
we’ll show You already the house half –
half finished.

03:08:31.259 --> 03:08:35.225
Shri Mataji: Good. [Yogi: Yes] You see,
what a miracle:

03:08:35.426 --> 03:08:39.882
this one we planned in five minutes,
didn’t we? Yogi: Yes, Shri Mataji.

03:08:40.298 --> 03:08:45.315
Shri Mataji: Better show Mister Shrivastava
[to] see how I planned it.

03:08:45.516 --> 03:08:50.049
They were all struggling with planning,
planning, planning:

03:08:51.543 --> 03:08:54.920
and really, in really five minutes.
Yogi: I’m sorry, Mother…

03:08:55.121 --> 03:09:01.901
Shri Mataji: Eh? No, no it’s all right,
see, everybody had to learn through that.

03:09:06.657 --> 03:09:12.035
What’s that? Now. Guido: Some presents
from Italy. Shri Mataji: Why, from Italy?

03:09:12.236 --> 03:09:19.238
I’ve not been to Italy so far, so much,
you see, it’s too much for Me.

03:09:27.349 --> 03:09:31.620
I don’t want to break it, it’s so nicely
done.

03:09:48.152 --> 03:09:49.898
That’s too much.
Guido: No, no, no.

03:09:50.099 --> 03:09:53.567
Shri Mataji: No, no, no, no, what, it’s too
much. It’s too much, just see, imagine.

03:09:53.775 --> 03:09:58.582
Just imagine, this is too much. How could
you give such a lot to Me?

03:09:58.783 --> 03:10:01.663
See this.

03:10:02.847 --> 03:10:06.890
It’s too much. Oh God.

03:10:07.821 --> 03:10:11.293
Are diamonds? These are diamonds?
Guido: Yes, yes, Shri Mataji.

03:10:11.494 --> 03:10:15.282
Shri Mataji: Oh God, I mean, I just
imagine, this is too much.

03:10:15.483 --> 03:10:19.077
Can you do that? Oh God.

03:10:19.342 --> 03:10:22.842
