03:10:23.043 --> 03:10:27.220
No, it’s too much, I mean, it’s too much
really.

03:10:27.450 --> 03:10:30.533
Yogi: Mother, he needs the blessings
of Lakshmi for his ashram!

03:10:30.734 --> 03:10:35.412
You need, definitely you need, isn’t it?

03:10:35.978 --> 03:10:40.363
Guido: We had to thank (?) the great
Architect, who planned the ashram.

03:10:40.588 --> 03:10:44.532
Shri Mataji: Ah, this is for architectural
work!

03:10:46.570 --> 03:10:50.803
