“I’m the best Planner”.

03:10:55.825 --> 03:10:58.906
Thank you very much, thank you,
it’s beautiful, it’s too much.

03:10:59.107 --> 03:11:03.322
Guido: This is for France.
Shri Mataji: Ah! This is the gratitude.

03:11:03.531 --> 03:11:07.987
