the Void is…

03:11:12.782 --> 03:11:14.192
Shri Mataji: Really, from where do they
come in?

03:11:14.393 --> 03:11:16.248
Guido: standing in the water element.
From Volterra.

03:11:16.449 --> 03:11:22.113
Shri Mataji: Eh God, just imagine! Let Me
have a pair - just now from there.

03:11:22.314 --> 03:11:26.083
Guido: You were talking about koshas and -
Atma and Jivatma.

03:11:26.284 --> 03:11:30.598
Shri Mataji: Can you imagine such a thing?
Who did that?

03:11:30.799 --> 03:11:34.172
Guido: It’s Parvati.

03:11:37.433 --> 03:11:42.618
Shri Mataji: But I’m surprised, yes!
Just imagine!

03:11:42.834 --> 03:11:49.923
Guido: All seven then. With the Gods,
the petals, from Mooladhara.

03:11:50.494 --> 03:11:52.028
Shri Mataji: Can you imagine!

03:11:52.229 --> 03:11:54.905
Guido: And You were talking about this
glass, saying that we have to become…

03:11:55.106 --> 03:11:59.915
Shri Mataji: And this is like a…
Guido: … pure, to reflect the Atma.

03:12:01.499 --> 03:12:07.589
Shri Mataji: I didn’t have anything
in My hand! Haven’t. Nothing.

03:12:10.279 --> 03:12:16.099
That’s like a Kundalini, is like.
Cannot be My bangles, were here.

03:12:16.300 --> 03:12:19.279
Guido: No, no, no, Shri Mataji, just You
were talking about this glass,

03:12:19.480 --> 03:12:26.092
and how we have to be like this water
to reflect Atma.

03:12:26.293 --> 03:12:30.045
Shri Mataji: Yes, I tell you. Really!
Can’t believe it!

03:12:30.246 --> 03:12:34.896
Show this one, this is a remarkable
photograph, I must say.

03:12:35.534 --> 03:12:39.261
